node.text:
Do you know what these clouds are called? 👇

☁️ Mammatus clouds are some of the most unusual and distinctive clouds formations with a series of bulges or pouches emerging from the base of a cloud. The shape of mammatus formations can vary widely; from the classic protruding shape, to a more elongated tube hanging from the cloud above.
Which is most impressive?

📷
1. @beautyandruin 
2. @jay_a_daley 
3. @iwata77 
4. @homegroenphotography 
5. @bokovoyphotography 
6. @theoriginalajaxjones

node.text:
Would you ride this trail? 🤙💥 Outstandingly filmed by @brendog1 with his friend @odub_23 in the front line.

This island is the main one of the Madeira archipelago, an autonomous region of Portugal, off Africa’s northwest coast bathed by the Atlantic Ocean. It's famous for its endless footpaths but this place has a whole range of mountain bike trails, if you are an advanced biker steep terrains with coastal views or flatter paths for beginners, this spot offers rides that suit all. 🙌🏼

Dotted around the island are wineries producing fortified Madeira wine. On the south coast, the capital, Funchal, is known for its 16th-century cathedral.

Would you dare conquer this trail? 🔥 Tag someone who would!

📽 @brendog1 w/ @odub_23
📍Madeira island, Portugal

Tag a bestie you would try this with! 🤯🔥

📽 @jessica_juarezz
